# CDP Data Engineering — Code Ownership
# Each line maps a file pattern to one or more owners.
# Owners are automatically requested for review on PRs.

# Data model changes need senior review
src/storage/models/                 @senior-data-engineer

# Identity resolution is critical path
src/processing/identity_*           @senior-data-engineer @data-scientist

# Privacy/GDPR code needs compliance review
src/privacy/                        @senior-data-engineer @compliance-lead

# AI/ML changes need ML team review
src/ml/                             @senior-data-engineer @ml-engineer

# Infrastructure changes need DevOps review
docker-compose.yml                  @senior-data-engineer @devops
Dockerfile                          @senior-data-engineer @devops
.github/workflows/                  @senior-data-engineer @devops

# Everything else — any data engineering team member
*                                   @data-engineering-team
